News.Title: Brace Port Logistics Secures 1 Billion Rupee Contract for Freight Forwarding and Logistics Services
News.Summary: Brace Port Logistics has been awarded a significant contract for freight forwarding and logistics services. The contract is valued at approximately 1 billion rupees, marking a substantial business opportunity for the company.
